quran[17]{c,v,t}:
  103,1,"lbut ko Masa,"
  103,2,"Ka Mata-an! A so manga Manosiya na matatago dun ko ka­logi,"
  103,3,"Inonta so Miyamaratiyaya, go pinggalubuk iran so manga pipiya, go ini pamagosiyata iran so bunar, go ini pamagosiyata iran so kaphan­tang."
  104,1,"Sangat a siksa, a ruk o omani Taliyanta-an, a makasodi,"
  104,2,"A so Miyanimo sa tamok na miyatamanon magitong,"
  104,3,"Tatarima-an niyan sa Mata­ an! A so tamok iyan na miyabaloi niyan sukaniyan a kakal!"
  104,4,"Gunuki niyan noto, Mata-an a Phoshangun ndun ko makaroput;"
  104,5,"Na antawa-a i miyakandao Ruka o antona-a so makaroput?"
  104,6,"So Apoi o Allah, a pakakaka­dugun,"
  104,7,"So pushokhayao ko manga poso:"
  104,8,"Mata-an naya! A si-i kiran mikolob,"
  104,9,"Si-i ko manga pasuk a manga rarawa."
  105,1,"Bangka da Katokawi so iniki­diya o Kadnan Ka ko khimangaruk ko Gadiya?"
  105,2,"Ba Niyan nda tagowa so An­tangan niran a marata si-i ko kalo­gi?"
  105,3,"Go biyotawanan Niyan siran sa manga Papanok a khirurungkap."
  105,4,"A Puphangolog kiran sa Ator a pho-on ko lipao a kiyomba;"
  105,5,"Na biyaloi Niyan siran a miya­kairing ko pur a kiyan (a olud)?"